Sartorius
Sartorius has been a leading innovator of scales, balances and other weighing equipment for over 150 years. Their commitment to quality and accuracy shows in the production of their top of the line products. Data Weighing Systems has been selling and providing services for Sartorius scales and balances since 1973.  Let us use our experience to help you better utilize your existing Sartorius scales or help you choose the best new product.  Call 1-800-750-6842 for immediate assistance.

